videos.description: Florida freshman Scottie Lewis swats Paul Scruggs' shot attempt off the backboard as the first half comes to a close in the Charleston Classic Championship.
videos.headline: Florida's Lewis rejects Scruggs' shot attempt to end 1st half

videos.description: Naji Marshall sends the ball up ahead to Quentin Goodin who capitalizes with a nice layup vs. Florida.

videos.description: Quentin Goodin takes the cross-court pass from Naji Marshall and pulls up for a 3-pointer to bring Xavier within five points of Florida late.
videos.headline: Goodin's 3-pointer pulls Xavier within 5 late
